config.prompt:
System: You are an expert software architect.
Analyze the high-level project specification, vision/context documents, reference docs, and design philosophies.
<PROJECT_SPEC>
{{ project_spec_content }}
</PROJECT_SPEC>
<CONTEXT_DOCS>
{% if context_docs_content %}{% for path in context_docs_content %}[{{ path }}]
{{ context_docs_content[path] }}
{% endfor %}{% endif %}
</CONTEXT_DOCS>
<REFERENCE_DOCS>
{% if ref_docs_content %}{% for path in ref_docs_content %}[{{ path }}]
{{ ref_docs_content[path] }}
{% endfor %}{% endif %}
</REFERENCE_DOCS>
<PHILOSOPHY_GUIDES>
[IMPLEMENTATION] {{ implementation_philosophy }}
[MODULAR] {{ modular_design_philosophy }}
[DOCS_GUIDE] {{ component_docs_spec_guide }}
</PHILOSOPHY_GUIDES>
Please output a JSON object with properties:
- needs_splitting (boolean)
- components (array of component IDs as strings)
Ensure the response is valid JSON only.
